{"tid":2492310,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"點解決頭瘡問題？","createTime":"2021-04-17T04:32:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T05:18:58.000Z","uid":34813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"306f2ccf0029a3e8b1028ce17d0b97f2d4fa49ab","tid":2492310,"uid":34813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:32:57.000Z","msg":"個頭生好多頭瘡點攪，呢個問題困擾咗我好多年"},{"pid":"432bf8fffdbae960d17603e360607e12150fba0b","tid":2492310,"uid":150973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:33:31.000Z","msg":"真係好難搞"},{"pid":"28218bd44ba397d032bcf30eb5a445a726d4eae5","tid":2492310,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:33:56.000Z","msg":"去買D抗真菌洗頭水試下<br />\n每星期用一兩次左右<br />\n五分鐘先沖水"},{"pid":"3d8c094f4f1d35860dea894e4851c016b917eb9f","tid":2492310,"uid":262335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:37:09.000Z","msg":"買枝t-GEL洗頭"},{"pid":"11ca01008904f3458cab5fcdc808b1c82d5d8ce4","tid":2492310,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:42:11.000Z","msg":"個個唔同，但凡係同頭皮，頭瘡有關都一定有人會落嘴頭叫你買抗真菌洗頭水。<br />\n<br />\n我自已就係換左洗頭水同日日用護髮素(5分鐘)，就有明顯功效<br />\n牌子係med字頭, 要用補濕或去頭皮既款， 所有萬寧款勿試<br />\n注意水溫唔可以熱<br />\n一星期內見效<br />\n<br />\n早上既頭皮碎愈來愈細，得番1粒點咁細，當做係正常皮膚死皮<br />\n<br />\n晚上洗完頭狂搓都無太多碎片。"},{"pid":"89c5f217b14c5f9a617981817958a97ff296d3ee","tid":2492310,"uid":69158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:14:07.000Z","msg":"煩左好多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728eaa0db45911c2923140d68f9018d124db54b7","tid":2492310,"uid":130177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:14:55.000Z","msg":"光頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好返再留"},{"pid":"b4b240876c0af3afa45e1d32384f2f0f9d7231ae","tid":2492310,"uid":117722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:18:58.000Z","msg":"成因係dht"}]}